WEBVTT

00:06.440 --> 00:10.110 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Good evening.
I'm Hari Sreenivasan. Gwen Ifill
and Judy Woodruff are away.

00:10.110 --> 00:13.614 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
