British report points the finger
at Russian President Vladimir

00:13.614 --> 00:18.652 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Putin for the radioactive
poisoning of a former KGB agent.

00:18.652 --> 00:22.356 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Also ahead: what Republican
presidential candidate Rand Paul
says are the differences between

00:22.356 --> 00:25.492 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
