00:34.701 --> 00:39.706 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And how a
place can inspire genius in its
people.

00:39.706 --> 00:42.910 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICARDO HAUSMANN, Harvard Center
for International Development:
Genius is not really about
individuals.

00:42.910 --> 00:46.313 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
