ice on untreated roads.
Thousands of commuters,
including President

01:59.953 --> 02:04.524 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Obama's motorcade, were
stuck in long backups.

02:04.524 --> 02:09.563 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Secretary of State John Kerry
acknowledged today that Iran may
use money from sanctions

02:09.563 --> 02:14.935 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
