country is receiving billions of
dollars in newly unfrozen
assets,

02:14.935 --> 02:19.139 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
in exchange for curbing
its nuclear program.

02:19.139 --> 02:23.310 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On CNBC today, Kerry said
there's no way to stop funds
flowing to the hard-line Iran
Revolutionary

02:23.310 --> 02:25.812 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Guard Corps, for example.

02:25.812 --> 02:32.185 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN KERRY, U.S. Secretary of
State: I think that some of it
will end up in the hands of

02:32.185 --> 02:38.792 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the IRGC or other entities, some
of which are labeled terrorists.
To some degree, I'm

02:38.792 --> 02:44.398 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
not going to sit here and tell
you that every component of that
can be prevented. But I

02:44.398 --> 02:51.872 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
