Davos, Switzerland, at the World
Economic Summit. He said he
hopes

02:58.745 --> 03:03.650 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Iran will put sanctions money
into rebuilding its economy. But
several Senate Republicans

03:03.650 --> 03:08.055 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
