Hassan Rouhani appealed for free
and fair elections next

03:13.226 --> 03:17.631 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
month. Thousands of moderate
candidates, who would support
Rouhani's reform agenda, have

03:17.631 --> 03:23.336 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
been disqualified by the
Guardian Council, made up of
Islamic clerics and jurists. The

03:23.336 --> 03:27.774 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
council ruled they were not
loyal enough to the ruling
system.

03:27.774 --> 03:32.245 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Pakistan observed a nationwide
day of mourning today for 21
people killed at a university

03:32.245 --> 03:36.783 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
by Taliban attackers. Students
held a protest and vigil in
Islamabad, urging the government

03:36.783 --> 03:41.988 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to do more to fight extremism.
They carried signs and lit
candles to honor the dead.

03:41.988 --> 03:47.727 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: The fact that such
incidents continue to happen and
that these terror groups
continue

03:47.727 --> 03:57.204 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to act with such impunity is
clear evidence of the fact that
this state is willfully being

03:57.204 --> 04:00.207 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
negligent of its duties.

04:00.207 --> 04:03.210 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Pakistani army
officials say yesterday's attack
was orchestrated from

04:03.210 --> 04:07.280 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
inside neighboring Afghanistan.

04:07.280 --> 04:13.353 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
