had been to Iran, Iraq, Syria or
Sudan in the last five

04:38.478 --> 04:43.583 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
years. An announcement today
said journalists, aid workers
and others may still be allowed

04:43.583 --> 04:49.489 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to enter the U.S. without visas.
The new requirements had
prompted objections from
European states.

04:49.489 --> 04:55.061 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And on Wall Street, stocks
managed a rebound, as oil prices
surged higher, and the European

04:55.061 --> 04:60.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Central Bank raised hopes for
additional stimulus efforts. The
Dow Jones industrial average

04:60.000 --> 05:06.072 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
