22:12.765 --> 22:15.501 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
SEN. RAND PAUL: I
think very much so.

22:15.501 --> 22:19.939 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think, when the NSA, when it
was discovered that the NSA was
collecting all of our phone

22:19.939 --> 22:23.842 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
