bipartisan commissions have
looked at it and said, you know
what?

22:36.722 --> 22:41.427 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We haven't stopped any terrorist
attacks by doing this. Now, I do
think, since the recent

22:41.427 --> 22:44.763 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
