like, oh, what are we going to
do? How do we protect ourselves?

22:44.763 --> 22:48.334 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
But I think there is a
significant amount of people in
my party who do believe, you

22:48.334 --> 22:52.037 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
