environment because people are
fearful.

22:59.311 --> 23:02.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: You're running for
your Senate seat at the same
time as you run for the
nomination.

23:02.615 --> 23:08.654 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A couple things that raises.
