23:13.092 --> 23:16.428 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEN. RAND PAUL: I wouldn't be
the first. Paul Ryan ran last
year, and ran for both Congress

23:16.428 --> 23:17.363 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
