23:17.796 --> 23:18.931 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Joe Lieberman.

23:18.931 --> 23:21.333 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
SEN. RAND PAUL:
LBJ, Joe Lieberman.

23:21.333 --> 23:26.605 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, I think there's a long list
of people who have run for two
offices. And it turns

23:26.605 --> 23:29.508 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
out that that is the way -- the
only way forward for me to put
the message forward and become

23:29.508 --> 23:31.810 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
