of the Donald Trumpism. I think
he's trying to one-up Donald

23:42.588 --> 23:45.090 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Trump on how tough
he's going to be.

23:45.090 --> 23:49.261 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But, really, we ought to think
through the ramifications of
what happens in the Middle

23:49.261 --> 23:54.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
East, because, so often, our
interventions in the Middle East
have led to consequences

23:54.066 --> 23:56.568 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that were unintended, but,
actually, I think, have made us
less safe.

23:56.568 --> 24:00.372 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Senator Rand Paul,
good luck on the campaign trail.

24:00.372 --> 24:05.144 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Thank you very much.

24:05.144 --> 24:11.817 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
SEN. RAND PAUL:
