made this week, and not the
usual records book statistic
that

24:35.774 --> 24:38.877 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
sports announcers
spout on Sunday.

24:38.877 --> 24:43.849 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
